These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
City: liverpool, venice
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, alhambra
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, video-games
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, motorbike
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
6. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| City      | venice      | liverpool |
| Cigar          | alhambra      | fonseca       |
| Hobby         | video-games | collecting  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | begonia      |
| Transport   | car       | motorbike      |
| Pet         | fish    | rabbit       |

