There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, orange
1. the german is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
2. the malaysian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the german is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
6. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House          | townhouse | cape-cod |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | writing  |
| Nationality           | german      | malaysian  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | cola      |
| Cigar           | aristoff     | prince    |
| Color     | purple  | orange     |

